---
title: Chicken & Potatoes with Cheddar Sauce Elevated Dinners. Impressively Easy.
description: Our chefs are always working on ways to get you dinner faster, fresher, and tastier all the time. This addition to our Fast & Fresh lineup delivers garlicky seared chicken cutlets with tender steamed potatoes all smothered in a rich, velvety cheddar cheese sauce. On the side is a generous salad of mixed greens dressed in tangy Greek vinaigrette and studded with crisp, nutty sunflower seeds and chewy dried cherries to round it all out. And just like that, you’ve got another 15-minute winner dinner on your hands.
